<subSubSection id="2D5C250A1D1DA7366965829559D3B9BD" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" type="conservation status">
<paragraph id="5DC79026023BDDA46C8A3F6158403965" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Conservation status in Cameroon.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0056087CBDEAFD883E91B2137621FF71" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
<taxonomicName id="42833780B71FDD193FA6C3B8034CA75C" authorityName="Jacq. - Fel., Bull. Mus. Natl. Hist. Nat., B, Adansonia Ser. 4, 3 (2): 143" authorityYear="1981" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Calvoa" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Calvoa stenophylla" order="Myrtales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="stenophylla">
<emphasis id="F815B9E823ED308622223BEEF19C16F5" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Calvoa stenophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is listed on http://www.iucnredlist.org as Endangered (
<bibRefCitation id="9A24CC3DA49F4D8FD3E08BAF3D0DF55C" author="Cheek, M" journalOrPublisher="ZooKeys" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" refId="B11" refString="Cheek, M, 2015. Calvoastenophylla. The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species 2015: e.T202776A2752734. [Downloaded on 09 August 2018]" title="Calvoastenophylla. The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species 2015: e. T 202776 A 2752734. [Downloaded on 09 August 2018]" year="2015">Cheek 2015</bibRefCitation>
). The species was assessed as Critically Endangered (
<bibRefCitation id="CF6AB0250A7295A832BD0B7AFB7DD192" author="Onana, JM" journalOrPublisher="Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" refId="B66" refString="Onana, JM, Cheek, M, 2011. Red data list of the flowering plants of Cameroon: IUCN Global Assessments. Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew" title="Red data list of the flowering plants of Cameroon: IUCN Global Assessments." year="2011">Onana and Cheek 2011</bibRefCitation>
), since it was known from only one locality and the associated threats at the time. 
<bibRefCitation id="02A97105DB4C1CA3538D68EB7D71E519" author="Cheek, M" journalOrPublisher="ZooKeys" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" refId="B11" refString="Cheek, M, 2015. Calvoastenophylla. The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species 2015: e.T202776A2752734. [Downloaded on 09 August 2018]" title="Calvoastenophylla. The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species 2015: e. T 202776 A 2752734. [Downloaded on 09 August 2018]" year="2015">Cheek (2015)</bibRefCitation>
reassessed the species, globally as Endangered, since the number of localities has increased to two, and area of occupancy of 8 km2. The second locality is in Equatorial Guinea (
<bibRefCitation id="0A210DA03A24564EF156C8BB06485FEB" author="Cheek, M" journalOrPublisher="ZooKeys" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" refId="B11" refString="Cheek, M, 2015. Calvoastenophylla. The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species 2015: e.T202776A2752734. [Downloaded on 09 August 2018]" title="Calvoastenophylla. The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species 2015: e. T 202776 A 2752734. [Downloaded on 09 August 2018]" year="2015">Cheek 2015</bibRefCitation>
). In Cameroon, the species is only known from one locality and the area of occupancy is about 4 km2. The extent of occurrence (EOO) is estimated at 1 km2, following the IUCN preferred grid cell size for aquatic organisms (
<bibRefCitation id="419E6D707E31CBEE351AE04A6D53B2B2" author="IUCN" journalOrPublisher="Tropical Conservation Science" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" publicationUrl="http://jr.iucnredlist.org/documents/RedListGuidelines.pdf" refId="B57" refString="IUCN, 2013. Guidelines for using the IUCN Red List Categories and Criteria. Version 10.1. http://jr.iucnredlist.org/documents/RedListGuidelines.pdf" title="Guidelines for using the IUCN Red List Categories and Criteria. Version 10.1." url="http://jr.iucnredlist.org/documents/RedListGuidelines.pdf" year="2013">IUCN 2013</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="6B841504B8478979AFD7AC9011CB5D2D" author="IUCN Standards and Petitions Subcomittee" journalOrPublisher="Tropical Conservation Science" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" publicationUrl="http://www.iucnredlist.org/documents/RedListGuidelines.pdf" refId="B58" refString="IUCN Standards and Petitions Subcomittee, 2017. Guidelines for Using the IUCN Red List Categories and Criteria. Version 13. http://www.iucnredlist.org/documents/RedListGuidelines.pdf" title="Guidelines for Using the IUCN Red List Categories and Criteria. Version 13." url="http://www.iucnredlist.org/documents/RedListGuidelines.pdf" year="2017">2017</bibRefCitation>
). This was used by 
<bibRefCitation id="2905E6B38EAC885C1E3FEBCBFFBF589F" DOI="https://doi.org/10.1007/s12225-015-9559-8" author="Cheek, M" journalOrPublisher="Kew Bulletin" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" pagination="10 - 15" refId="B12" refString="Cheek, M, Poveda, LL, Darbyshire, I, 2015. Ledermanniella lunda sp. nov. (Podostemaceae) of Lunda Norte, Angola. Kew Bulletin 70 (1): 10 - 15, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1007/s12225-015-9559-8" title="Ledermanniella lunda sp. nov. (Podostemaceae) of Lunda Norte, Angola." url="https://doi.org/10.1007/s12225-015-9559-8" volume="70" year="2015">Cheek et al. (2015)</bibRefCitation>
in assessing the conservation status of 
<taxonomicName id="3E9DAC96F45DA4E3CB2BB7146AF74B61" authorityName="Cheek" authorityYear="2015" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Podostemaceae" genus="Ledermanniella" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Ledermanniella lunda" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lunda">
<emphasis id="6603278C7387F92EE2715D2AC96C679E" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Ledermanniella lunda</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Cheek (
<taxonomicName id="F4DA5C9C7B78EF0C2BF41690E4E15F7E" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Podostemaceae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Podostemaceae" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="genus">Podostemaceae</taxonomicName>
) from Angola. The main threats are forest logging and agriculture activities. Based on these threats, and the continuous decline of vegetation in the area, extent and /or quality of habitat 
<taxonomicName id="9A995178F59F0A8FE1157AC23964A9F9" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Oxalidaceae" genus="C." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="C. stenophylla" order="Oxalidales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" phylum="Magnoliophyta" rank="species" species="stenophylla">
<emphasis id="95B836B8177CBE4D925547A289B766A0" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">C. stenophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is here assessed, as Critically Endangered. IUCN Red List Category: 
<emphasis id="4D5B95AE6BB6591353F1C791C75FE4DA" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Critically Endangered CRB2ab (ii, iii).</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
